			<img class="image" src="assets/careers1.jpg" alt="" />
			<p>HCJI Career Forum is a 4-day series of events held before and during the annual Boston Career Forum (BCF) that serve as an opportunity for Harvard students and students who have been involved in Harvard programs in the past, to interact and network with companies in a more personal and casual environment.</p>
