			</div>
			<img class="image" src="assets/campus1.jpg" alt="" />
			<p>HCJI Explore welcomes junior and senior high school students from all over Japan to "explore" the life at Harvard. We provide them with unique opportunities through our on-campus tours, presentations and workshops. All of these programs are created and coordinated by HCJI members and other Harvard students.</p>
