			</div>
			<img class="image" src="assets/dinner.jpg" alt="" />
			<p>The Dinner Series, held in collaboration with the Reishcauer Institute of Japan Studies, invites renown professors and postdoctoral fellows to a specially catered dinner with 10 to 15 undergraduate students. We have been honored to have Professor Christine Yano, Dr. Nicolas Cisterna, and Professor Daniel Smith as our guests in 2014-2015.</p>
